articles.text:
Nigerians on social media have berated President Muhammadu Buhari’s Igbo outfit while he visited Imo state on Thursday.

Earlier today, President Buhari arrived Imo state where he commissioned several projects done by the state governor, Hope Uzodinma.

Buhari was received by dignitaries at the Sam Mbakwe Airport in Imo state.

See some reactions gathered below:

@Heisjoseph wrote, “Unrelated, but the tailor that styled President Buhari no fit make heaven.”

Another Twitter user named @VictorIsrael_ wrote,“It’s so Obvious that President Buhari isn’t welcomed to Imo state because even his Trouser refuse to touch the ground.”

@realDewoye tweeted, “Muhammadu Buhari is the only person I know who can wear what is supposed to be a special attire in the Igbo culture & still look like an almajiri in the dress.”

@ICON wrote, “DSS should arrest the tailor.”
